  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 09\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c 03\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "09 million gold with 03 boxes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "03 suspects were taken into the custody of Navy in Pesala along with gold worth more than 09 million rupees which they tried to take out of the country illegally.",
        "The Sri Lanka Navy carried out a special search yesterday (25th) night in the sea coast off Kurusapadu area, Pesala, Mannar.",
        "In an operation, three persons suspected of trying to smuggle 470 grams of gold and a Valampuri out of the country were taken into custody by the Navy.",
        "Sri Lanka Naval Ships of North Central Naval Command deployed Coastal Patrol Vessels belonging to Tammanna to Mannar, Pesale Krusapadu area",
        "Suspicious dinghies left the Kurusapadu beach during a special search operation on the night of July 25, 2022 on the coast beyond.",
        "A vessel was observed and inspected. There, the dinghy was taken into custody along with three suspects along with a Valampuri and an amount of 470 grams of gold suspected to have been illegally taken to Meratin.",
        "The market value of the gold seized by the Navy is believed to be over nine million rupees.",
        "During this operation, the suspects who were taken into custody by the Navy were identified as residents of Puttalam and Paisal, between the ages of 24 and 39, and the suspects, Ratrang, Valampuria and the dinghy are to be handed over to the Jaffna Customs Office for further legal proceedings."
      ],
